<view class="container">
	<view class="page__bd">
		<view class="weui-cells__title">
			<text>原文</text>
			<text >编号：12345</text>
		</view>
		<view class="weui-cells weui-cells_after-title">
            <view class="complain_main">机场大巴周围很多黑车，每次都很受困扰，希望可以改善改善改善改善改善改善改善改善</view>
            <view class="weui-uploader__bd" style="padding: 25rpx">
            	<view class="weui-uploader__files" id="uploaderFiles">
            		<block wx:for="{{files}}" wx:key="*this">
            			<view class="weui-uploader__file" bindtap="previewImage" id="{{item}}">
            				<image class="weui-uploader__img" src="{{item}}" mode="aspectFill" />
            			</view>
            		</block>
            		<view class="weui-uploader__file">
            			<image class="weui-uploader__img" src="../../../../images/swiper.png" mode="aspectFill" />
            		</view>
            		<view class="weui-uploader__file">
            			<image class="weui-uploader__img" src="../../../../images/swiper.png" mode="aspectFill" />
            		</view>
            		<view class="weui-uploader__file">
            			<image class="weui-uploader__img" src="../../../../images/swiper.png" mode="aspectFill" />
            		</view>
            		<view class="weui-uploader__file">
            			<image class="weui-uploader__img" src="../../../../images/swiper.png" mode="aspectFill" />
            		</view>
            	</view>
            </view>
            <view class="complain_no"><text>2018年3月4日</text></view>
		</view>
		<view class="weui-cells__title">客户回复</view>
		<view class="weui-cells weui-cells_after-title">
			<view class="complain_main">尊敬的客户您好，关于您提出的问题，我们已经加强了管理，并进行了解决，感谢您的建议，祝您旅途愉快</view>
			<view class="complain_no"><text>2018年3月4日</text></view>
		</view>
	</view>
	<view class="rate">
		<view style="text-align: center;" ><text>请为本次服务进行打分</text></view>
		<cxRate id='cxRate' star='{{star}}' bindchange='handleChange'>
		</cxRate>
	</view>
	<button class="sureBtn" bindtap="sendStar">提交评价</button>
</view>
